  "title": "Part-time Retail Executive @ Orchard/HabourFront (Up to $15/hr)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🤎 6 Months Commitment<br>\n🤎 Training Provided<br>\n🤎 Staff Discount<br>\n🤎Incremental Pay Based on Contributed Hours<br>\n<br>\n💰Salary: </strong>$10 - $15/hr<strong><br>\n<br>\n📍Working Location: </strong>ION / VivoCity<br>\n<strong><br>\nWork Schedule:</strong><br>\n2 - 3 Days Per Week (1 Weekend Required)<strong><br>\n<br>\nOperations Hours:</strong><br>\n🕘Monday - Sunday<br>\n9:30 - 21:30 |10:30 - 22:30 |13:00 - 22:30<strong><br>\n<br>\nDuties:</strong><br>\n✔️ Manage day-to-day store operations, including inventory management and visual merchandising<br>\n✔️ Maintain the store’s cleanliness and overall presentation<br>\n✔️ Handle cashier duties<br>\n✔️ Conduct weekly stock-taking<br>\n✔️ Maintain excellent customer service standards, professionally resolving customer concerns and escalations<br>\n<br>\n📩 Interested candidates may send their resumes to<strong> hr@lovet.sg</strong><br>\n*Shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
